        {
            "text": "Conflict of interest statement: Antonio Costanzo has received speaker honoraria or grants for research from Abbvie, Almirall, Pfizer, Novartis, Lilly, UCB, Janssen. The other authors have no conflict of interest do disclose.",
            "cite_spans": [],
